12
00:05:21,331 --> 00:05:46,677
And the last bullet point on that one, it says requested new staff programs or services. I was just wondering, is this requested new staff program or services after a preliminary process in the mayor's office or just from the department submitted to the mayor? Mr. Crafton. I think that's a great question. I think it's something we should discuss.

13
00:05:47,555 --> 00:06:16,259
and I think that's why we have the administration here as well. So I think it could be either, and I don't have a preference. Great, I was, yeah, just wondering about intent, but that's the only thing that's really stood out for me. I'm excited to take this on. Thank you, Councilor Sang, Councilor Collins. Thank you. I think my comments to start out with are not substantively different from what I've shared in previous subcommittee meetings on this topic. It's great to see this draft

