Yeah, where it came from is the meetings that we've had up to this point. We kind of put out a framework in February. We fleshed out that framework somewhat in March, and then based on the motions and resolutions, I filled that out and submitted it to the subcommittee and to you guys. So that's where it came from. It's not really

