understood. Yeah, and then that that's, you know, in some part, I was almost hoping to see a model that existed somewhere else so that we could contact that community and ask them questions and see what their systems are and see how they actually execute these things. The systems that are likely to hinder or I expect would hinder the city's ability to be able to execute on even a quarter of some of the things that are outlined in this ordinance, especially just even focusing on the first part,

