00:13:12,329 --> 00:13:36,342
what are all of the systems and resources that we need to put in place to even get to a point where we can have a process that's really fleshed out so we know our needs and how to get there. And I think, you know, speaking for myself, I won't speak for the subcommittee or for the full council, what those resources are and how quickly we can get them, totally open to discussion and putting stuff in here that says, hey,

