00:13:37,473 --> 00:14:02,498
If we determine that a piece of this is not doable, we'll let you know what we think we need to do it and how long we think it'll take for us to get the resources to make it possible. If I may. Thank you. I think I understand the basis and the intent to collect information and to be a part of the discussion.

