a future council may take issue with those issues, right? We don't know how a future council would view it. This council may be understanding because it was part of the implementation, hypothetically, but a future council may turn to the city and say, it's completely unreasonable that you can't provide these things when full well, it was known to the council that existed several years prior, but now it's five years later.

