I think we have a lot of precedent this term for taking ordinances and then saying, you know, what is reasonable here and I think we have a lot of precedent this term for saying, you know, this particular piece makes sense, it is achievable, but not next year, maybe in five years, not next year, maybe next August. I think that that's something that, you know, for myself, certainly willing to contemplate in the context of this ordinance and, you know, based on

