and then have the conversation of, is this something that we phase in? Is this something that we rephrase so that it's more clear that, you know, for myself, all of the parts of this ordinance where we say, if this isn't, if this data doesn't exist, that's fine, just tell us why. I think that's meant in really in good faith and not as a way to say,

