00:24:45,132 --> 00:25:14,056
Thank you, Councillor Sang. First, I just want to say I appreciate my draft being considered 100. I think it's at best B plus work. Well, thank you. I appreciate that. And I understand it is comprehensive. And that word shows up quite a few times in the draft itself. I think number one, I agree with a lot of what everyone has said here.

